{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"e2817c5d-1398-4688-94fa-c8076f9c76cc","name":"红旗一九六四年第一期","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/e2817c5d-1398-4688-94fa-c8076f9c76cc.pdf"],"article":{"title":"七律·人民解放军占领南京","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"首诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东毛电泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年四月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民解放军占领南京钟山风雨起茗黄，百万雄师过大江虎踞龙盘今胜昔，天翻地覆而慷。宜将剩勇追寇，不可沽名学霸王。天若有情天亦老，人间正道是桑。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":4}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}